text: Cicatrisestola flavicans is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1947. It is known from Argentina, Brazil, Bolivia and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Cicatrisestola flavicans. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1947
title: Cicatrisestola flavicans
